{"tid":112410,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Fg做左兩份工 想再轉","createTime":"2017-02-08T06:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T05:20:44.000Z","uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc90bc58999b9055e71fcd4d944ce1855405d43f","tid":112410,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"兩份都係返左三個月<br />\n第一份工 試完覺得自己唔適合呢行<br />\n第二份工 即係而家呢份 其實係ta<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但覺得入行無咩希望 應唔應該盡快轉行？"},{"pid":"caaf77d3e0204c5371a0d18104a551767143c35f","tid":112410,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩份都係返左三個月<br />\n第一份工 試完覺得自己唔適合呢行<br />\n第二份工 即係而家呢份 其實係ta<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但覺得入行無咩希望 應唔應該盡快轉行？</blockquote><br />\n講真 你自己有冇諗住做邊行<br />\n你咁樣轉法同大海撈針冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6641f03284530584fab8bed04fdfe6df83100f45","tid":112410,"uid":15140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"做TA  去教院讀番個文憑<br />\n有機做教畜wo"},{"pid":"2452a06600a2557c591fa3db70f8f812440f6c36","tid":112410,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"咁快放棄"},{"pid":"bbf1de5eaf0f9fe2467917caa665807dcdbfaf4d","tid":112410,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩份都係返左三個月<br />\n第一份工 試完覺得自己唔適合呢行<br />\n第二份工 即係而家呢份 其實係ta<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但覺得入行無咩希望 應唔應該盡快轉行？</blockquote><br />\n講真 你自己有冇諗住做邊行<br />\n你咁樣轉法同大海撈針冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想教書<br />\n第一份係補習社 小型 <br />\n都係想教日校 就做ta<br />\n岩岩in左教育文憑<br />\n但感覺應該無架喇<br />\n而我上手都係拎住個教育文憑做我呢個位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想放棄教書<br />\n<br />\n點會無諗想做乜<br />\n我讀呢科 個個問我第時係咪想教書<br />\n我就無當年中學畢業天真 真係想教書所以揀呢科<br />\n唉<br />\n<br />\n利申 語文科"},{"pid":"bcd1d406073655fc611bd5c0f91ae6f2a451eed7","tid":112410,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做TA  去教院讀番個文憑<br />\n有機做教畜wo</blockquote><br />\n教院報左中學英文 interview都無"},{"pid":"b0c11de19fe71befb3aeaafcf8499f35335dd6d3","tid":112410,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁快放棄</blockquote><br />\n想放棄埋生命 <br />\n好撚垃圾<br />\n做Ta 中學生都睇你唔起"},{"pid":"a04ef88de38ef6cadbd2bd8db67efb144232da3d","tid":112410,"uid":15140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做TA  去教院讀番個文憑<br />\n有機做教畜wo</blockquote><br />\n教院報左中學英文 interview都無</blockquote><br />\n簡其他囉 咁多科簡<br />\n試下叫學校 放工教下班囉 帶下活動<br />\nBy the way 本生咩學歷先"},{"pid":"2254ee9b742850e15cf1c0feeda32e5aae6c7235","tid":112410,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做TA  去教院讀番個文憑<br />\n有機做教畜wo</blockquote><br />\n教院報左中學英文 interview都無</blockquote><br />\n簡其他囉 咁多科簡<br />\n試下叫學校 放工教下班囉 帶下活動<br />\nBy the way 本生咩學歷先</blockquote><br />\n報左通識 沒有回音<br />\n帶隊真係好撚on9<br />\n今日帶 有兩個南亞學生 <br />\n好撚唔服從 鬧佢又係度笑同講家鄉話<br />\n好驚佢唔知對我做乜 唉 唔想再對住呢班人<br />\n<br />\n學歷三大英文 <br />\nDse本科有* 但gpa好柒<br />\n再講驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b5b785d86cf27c1c08d867540b99820637f428","tid":112410,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁快放棄</blockquote><br />\n想放棄埋生命 <br />\n好撚垃圾<br />\n做Ta 中學生都睇你唔起</blockquote><br />\n唔好<br />\nMe睇得起你<br />\n咁後生大把工轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6632c1c08a96f19602fcf83b16de680038825ec2","tid":112410,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁快放棄</blockquote><br />\n想放棄埋生命 <br />\n好撚垃圾<br />\n做Ta 中學生都睇你唔起</blockquote><br />\n唔好<br />\nMe睇得起你<br />\n咁後生大把工轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時先退休呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c498f9dd93f943f6dd162f82ac03ab3511cd4a03","tid":112410,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:43:24.000Z","msg":"有無興趣做補習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係補習社果種<br />\n係online edu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7a7d3e970210d5e32198cad577a38aee199da9","tid":112410,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無興趣做補習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係補習社果種<br />\n係online edu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補習真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你嗰隻係網上問功課嗰啲？"},{"pid":"9114fa6f37550103935a4e8e8dd5aecbd5b806e5","tid":112410,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁快放棄</blockquote><br />\n想放棄埋生命 <br />\n好撚垃圾<br />\n做Ta 中學生都睇你唔起</blockquote><br />\n唔好<br />\nMe睇得起你<br />\n咁後生大把工轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></